    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2114160/extras/f1a4d6d24da63b425f0f2bf0016cead0.avif?t=1771997226\" width=600 height=147 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2114160/extras/69bf3240ae00a0fe8b7a474f61f82b0a.avif?t=1771997226\" width=592 height=72 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong><i>从亡命之徒…</i></strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >罗宾渴望一个英雄的出现——家家户户正在挨饿，她的村庄工艺品可危，人民付不起税金，领主们却只顾自己。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >走进舍伍德森林时，她唯一确定的是：罗宾汉根本不存在。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >她还是徒然地等待那个不存在的英雄，或者自己披上这个传奇义贼的斗篷。她知道这条路危机重重，但无论如何，她已经决定自己赌上己的性命。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong><i>…到间谍</i></strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >罗宾并不孤独。女巫给她指引，小红帽给她希望。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >随着越来越多人追随她，罗宾意识到自己正处于一场叛乱风暴的中心。她谨慎、聪明，箭术出神入化……然而局势变幻莫测，太多人把希望寄托于她身上。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >她该信任谁？该冒哪些险？她的计划真的万无一失吗？</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>如果罗宾现在倒下，有多少人会因此丧命？</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2114160/extras/fc63e26eb74a2aa8594fc993b9299cc3.avif?t=1771997226\" width=592 height=72 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >🏹百合版本的罗宾汉 x 小红帽历险故事</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >💕多对百合角色</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >🎭换装变身 隐藏身份</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >🕵️‍♀️建立间谍网络</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >🐺奇幻民间传说</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >📚历史小说</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >🎮多款小游戏与解迷</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >🛣️ 双结局 + 支线角色结局</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >🖼️精美CG、背景、大角色阵容</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >🎼原创中世纪风格配乐</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >📖历史术语词汇表</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >📰额外内容：音乐播放器、CG 画廊、角色档案</p>",
